# shotAI builds/ships x64 and runs emulated on Windows-on-ARM (see docs/PLAN.md).
# The x64 Electron binary is fetched by scripts/postinstall-electron.mjs, because
# npm 11's allow-scripts allowlist blocks Electron's own (dependency) postinstall.
# Native-module x64 prebuilds (Phase 1) are handled with `electron-rebuild --arch x64`.
#
# NOTE: do NOT add arch= / target_arch= / runtime= here — npm 11 rejects them as
# "Unknown project config" and warns on every command. Arch is forced in the
# postinstall script instead.
